# Week 2
High context vs low context.

Monochronic VS Polychronic Cultures.
mono - time is lenear (norhen europa, japan). punctionality. optimise time.
poly - time as elastic (latin, india, china).

greeting, business card exchange,

# Week 3
The cross-cultural negotiator's dilemma.
1) The cliche - recognize, refrain.

Adaptation strategies:
1) Employ a third-party.
2) Induce counterpart to follow one's own script.
3) Embrace counterpart the counterpart's script.
4) Adapt to the counterpart script.
5) Improvise an approach.

